quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  33,63,"“Anthu akukufunsa za (kudza kwa) nthawi (ya tsiku la chitsiriziro). Nena: “Kuzindikira kwa nthawiyo kuli ndi Allah (Yekha). Nanga nchiyani chikudziwitse kuti nthawi ya chimaliziro iri pafupi?”"
  33,64,“Ndithu Allah wawatembelera osakhulupirira ndi kuwakonzera Moto woyaka kwambiri
  33,65,“Adzakhala nrmenemo nthawi yaitali. Sadzapeza bwenzi ngakhale mthandizi
  33,66,"“Tsiku limene nkhope zawo zikatembenuzidwa ku Moto (zikutenthedwa), uku akunena: “Kalanga ife! Tikadamumvera Allah ndi kumveranso Mtumiki (s.a.w), (sibwenzi tili m’chilangomu).”"
  33,67,"“Ndipo adzanena: “E Mbuye wathu! Ndithu ife tidamvera olemekezeka athu ndi akuluakulu athu, choncho adatisokeza njira.”"
  33,68,"“Mbuye wathu! Apatseni chilango pamwamba pa chilango ndipo atembelereni, kutembelera kwakukulu.”"
  33,69,“E inu amene mwakhulupirira! Musakhale monga amene adamvutitsa Mûsa; koma Allah adamuyeretsa kuzimene ankamnenera. Ndipo iye kwa Allah adali wolemekezeka
  33,70,"“E inu amene mwakhulupirira! Opani Allah (pokwaniritsa malamulo Ake, ndi kusiya zoletsedwa), ndipo nenani mawu olungama"
  33,71,"“Akukonzerani bwino zochita zanu ndi kukukhululukirani machimo anu. ndipo amene akumvera Allah ndi Mtumiki Wake, ndithu apambana; kupambana kwakukulu"
  33,72,“Ndithu Ife tidapereka udindo (otsatira malamulo) ku thambo ndi nthaka ndi mapiri; koma zidakana kuwusenza (udindowo); ndipo zidauopa. Koma munthu adawusenza; ndithu iye ngwachinyengo kwambiri ndiponso mbuli
  33,73,"“Kuti Allah adzawalange achiphamaso aamuna ndi aakazi, ndi opembedza mafano achimuna ndi achikazi ndi kuti adzawakhululukire okhulupirira achimuna ndi achikazi. Ndipo Allah Ngokhululuka kwabasi, Ngwachisoni chosatha"